## Prerequisites

* Bash 4.0+
* vcprompt - https://github.com/ericmeyer/vcprompt
* rvm
* git
* hg

## Use

* clone this repo into $HOME/.bash
* Add the following to your bash config file(s):
  * source $HOME/.bash/source_all
* Link the gitconfig and tmux.conf files
  * ln -s ~/.bash/.gitconfig .gitconfig
  * ln -s ~/.bash/.tmux.conf .tmux.conf
